docs.abstract: Iridium Communications says it will soon launch first batch of next-generation satellites on SpaceX Falcon 9 rocket; announcement comes three months after SpaceX rocket exploded in Cape Canaveral, Fla, destroying $200 million Israeli satellite; upcoming launch must be cleared by Federal Aviation Admin, which is currently reviewing company's investigation of September disaster.

docs.abstract: Thailand has begun implementation of voluntary program, created by country's prime minister, Gen Prayuth Chan-ocha, in which civil servants can attend exercise sessions during working hours; program is meant to address widespread physical idleness among country's youth and older citizens.
